usercssData.name: Github Tokyo Night
usercssData.author: fun840 .
usercssData.description: A Tokyo Night theme for GitHub, based on the Tokyo Night VSCode theme. It's not perfect, and the editor doesn't support as advanced syntax highlighting as VSCode, but it still looks pretty good.
